Package: orix
Version: $(VERSION)
Architecture: $(ARCH)
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libc6 (>= 2.17)
Description: High-performance package manager compatible with pnpm
 Orix is a blazing fast, disk space efficient package manager for Node.js.
 It creates a non-flat node_modules directory, handles dependency hoisting
 intelligently, and is fully compatible with the pnpm ecosystem.
